com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities
Class Collection

java.lang.Object
  com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities.Collection

public class Collection
extends java.lang.Object

Models a collection of entities as a local object. Collections are the primary way that entities are organized in API BaaS.
